div.mw1000.center-block
    div.panel.br-t.bw5.br-grey
        div.panel-body.pn
            div.p25.br-b
                h2.fw200.mb20.mt10 Organization Chart
            div.p25.bg-light
                p The directory allows you to view snap-shot of the organization chart based on a particular employee.
                hr.short.alt
                h3
                    i.fa.fa-sitemap.text-primary.fa-lg.pr10
                    | Employee View
                h4 Selecting an employee from the list will display the following:
                ul.fs14.list-spacing-10.mbn
                    li The employee's photo, name &amp; title
                    li The employee's manager (photo, name &amp; title)
                    li The employee's direct reports (photo, name &amp; title)
                h5 You can direct link to a particular employee's organization chart snap-shot by adding the employee ID at the end of the org chart url
                ul.fs14.list-spacing-10.mbn
                    li
                        a(ui-sref="employees.org-chart({'employee': '1209764'})") http://directory.liazon.corp/employees/org-chart/1209764
                hr.short.alt
                p Clicking on the employee will take you to the profile of that employee.
                p Clicking on the employee's manager will display the organization chart snap-shot for the manager.
                p Clicking on an employee's direct report will display the organization chart snap-shot for the direct report.
